<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Safeway cut to outperform.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Safeway cut to outperform.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Smith Barney downgraded Safeway Inc to outperform from buy, a Smith Barney source said.</p>
<p>-- Additional details of the rating change were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- Safeway said earlier on Thursday that a strike by its union in Canada may hurt sales and operating results.</p>
<p>-- Safeway lost 3-1/4 to 44-3/4.</p>
